The paper deals with online learning, multi-task learning, and coordination of learners, which are all topics that fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of convex constraints and projections also suggests a connection to optimization and convex optimization (cs.DS). The application of learning user preferences on a marketplace involves recommendation systems and user modeling, which could fall under social and information networks (cs.SI) or information theory (cs.IT).
